class code_SemperKI.modelFiles.projectModel.Project(*args, **kwargs)¶

Bases: django.db.models.Model

Project class.

ProjectID:

Unique ID for that project, primary key

ProjectStatus:

Current state of the project

Client:

The hashed ID of the client that created the project

ProjectDetails:

Details like name and such

CreatedWhen:

Automatically assigned date and time(UTC+0) when the entry is created

UpdatedWhen:

Date and time at which the entry was updated

AccessedWhen:

Last date and time the data was fetched from the database, automatically set
